{
  "stem": "24466.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't remember the names quite rightly.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And after the head of the ghetto, that was [?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Gentz. ?] He was a captain and a Jew, a captain in the-- in the Lithuanian army.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[SIGHS] There was another one.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The police was carrying on with the-- there was-- Judenrat was in the beginning-- so-- in beginning.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And after, the police took over.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Gentz ?] took over with other, other commandants.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I beg you?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was in the ghetto number one.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Selections, they had been in the number one, and the number one through.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And sending, then, we went to number two.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And after, to Ponary.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Selections.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[SPEAKING GERMAN] Something they find out, some other things, the big selections.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The fight?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That happens every-- no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't know about this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it happens.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we know about this, that it's going to make selections.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They want whatever's there, right and [INAUDIBLE] or-- and one went to Ponary.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The others went to work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First-- no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, I wouldn't say that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was actually-- it's very-- I got a schein.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So long as I was in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A schein, that is papers that I'm working for the-- in the tanneries.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, you know, that the products produced there, they are very essential in time for the war.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they were-- they were trying to have the people that they will-- It's hard-- For instance, somebody telled to-- tell me, all right, the Germans did out a good-- a good job because they were trying to give you work and to, to, to have this supply, you know, of-- to, to feed you and so on.",
      "word_count": 58
    }
  ],
